     * Deliver faster, smarter marketing.
       Built-in intelligence automatically surfaces your most valuable
       marketing insights so you can act quickly to achieve your goals.
     * Gain more control over your investments.
       Easily see what parts of your marketing are working and make
       informed decisions to improve performance — ensuring that you’re
       delivering quality experiences.
     * Understand your audience on a deeper level.
       Easily integrate and access your data to gain a deeper
       understanding of your customers and identify your most valuable
       audiences.
     * Share insights across your team.
       Make information and insights accessible to your entire enterprise
       so teams can work better together.

